prodNameC: 生物梅里埃乳膠凝集腦膜炎細菌測定試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
R1  H. influenzae type b latex:
Anti-H. influenzae type b serum (rabbit) (sodium merthiolate 0.2 g/l+sodium azide 1 g/l).
R2  Streptococcus pneumoniase omhi type latex:
Anti-S. pneumoniae serum (rabbit) (sodium merthiolate 0.2 g/l+sodium azide 1g/l).
R3  Neissria meningitides group A latex:
Anti-N. meningitides A serum (rabbit) (sodium merthiolate 0.2 g/l+sodium azide 1 g/l). 
R4  Neisseria meningitides group B/ Escherichia coli K1 latex:
Anti-N. meningitides B monoclonal antibody (mouse) (sodium merthiolate 0.2 g/l+sodium azide 1 g/l). 
R5  Neisseria meningitides group C latex:
Anti-N. meningitides C serum (rabbit) (sodium merthiolate 0.2 g/l+sodium azide 1g/l). 
R6  Positive control: (lyophilized)
Antigen extracts of H. influenzae b, S.pneumoniae, N.meningitides A, C, E.coli K1 (sodium merthiolate 0.1 g/l).
